3><\/div><!-- .section-title -->\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2016, Langmaster \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 100.000 h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">Trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 7 &#8211; 12 n\u0103m (t\u1eeb b\u1eadc ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc) \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh, trong \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 8.77% c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u01b0u lo\u00e1t, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 92.22% kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 giao ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, Langmaster \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Experiential Learning Cycle (vi\u1ebft t\u1eaft l\u00e0 ELC) c\u1ee7a TS David A.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">Kolb thu\u1ed9c \u0110H Hardvard \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c, th\u00f3i quen v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"\/lien-he\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button primary\"  >\n    <span>\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ecdc th\u1eed mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"col medium-5 small-12 large-5\"  ><div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_362405930\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img width=\"532\" height=\"474\" src=\"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/ketqua-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-