t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 90%;\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ed1n t\u1eeb, c\u00e1ch di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1t: b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1eadp trung suy ngh\u0129 b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecbch sang ti\u1ebfng Anh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 ch\u1eadm khi giao ti\u1ebfp.<\/span><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div><!-- .icon-box -->\n\t\n\t\n<div class=\"gap-element\" style=\"display:block; height:auto; padding-top:22px\" class=\"clearfix\"><\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-left text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 30px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"31\" height=\"30\" src=\"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/vande-2.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-reset\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%; color: #ffffff;\">Thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ebfng Anh: h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean lu\u00f4n s\u1ee3 sai khi n\u00f3i n\u00ean c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng nghe gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div><!-- .icon-box -->\n\t\n\t\n<div class=\"gap-element\" style=\"display:block; height:auto; padding-top:22px\" class=\"clearfix\"><\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-left text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 30px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"29\" height=\"32\" src=\"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/vande-3.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-