yle=\"font-size: 90%;\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00fac k\u1ebft kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh s\u1ebd d\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh l\u1ed1i t\u01b0 duy b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 trong giao ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. R\u00fat ng\u1eafn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c d\u1ecbch sang ti\u1ebfng Anh t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t khi t\u01b0 duy trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh giao ti\u1ebfp.<\/span><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div><!-- .icon-box -->\n\t\n\t\n<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  ><div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-left text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 50px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"62\" height=\"43\" src=\"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/lydo-2.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-reset\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">02. L\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng giao ti\u1ebfp th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c video, t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u th\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng giao ti\u1ebfp th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ea5t theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Cambridge v\u00e0 Oxford. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ELC s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng giao ti\u1ebfp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, g\u1ea7n g\u0169i nh\u1ea5t<\/span><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div><!-- .icon-box -->\n\t\n\t\n<div class=\"gap-element\" style=\"display:block; height:auto; padding-top:24px\" class=\"clearfix\"><\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-left text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 50px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"51\" height=\"47\" src=\"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/lydo-4.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-reset\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 90%; color: #ed1c24;\">04. Ng\u1eef \u00e2m v\u00e0 ng\u1eef \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea3n ng\u1eef<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a ELC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1eeb t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u th\u1ef1c, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh giao ti\u1ebfp ti\u1ebfng Anh, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean s\u1ebd n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t \u00e2m v\u00e0 ng\u1eef \u0111i\u1ec7u trong giao ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecba.<\/span><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div><!-- .icon-box -->\n\t\n\t\n<div class=\"gap-element\" style=\"display:block; height:auto; padding-top:24px\" class=\"clearfix\"><\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-left text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 50px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"48\" height=\"46\" src=\"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/lydo-6.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-reset\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 90%;\">06. Thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9, th\u00f3i quen h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">V\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ELC cung c\u1ea5p cho h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 gi\u00fap thay \u0111\u1ed5i tinh th\u1ea7n, th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/span><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div><!-- .icon-box -->\n\t\n\t\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><!-- .section-content -->\n\n\t\t\n<style scope=\"scope\">\n\n#section_1907333348 {\n  padding-top: 35px;\n  padding-bottom: 35px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_1914316372\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  \" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div><!-- .section-bg -->\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-875882233\">\n<div class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  ><div class=\"col-inner text-center\"  >\n<div class=\"container section-title-container\" ><h2 class=\"section-title section-title-center\"><b><\/b><span class=\"section-title-main\" style=\"font-size:110%;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ecdc th\u1eed mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><b><\/b><\/h2><\/div><!-- .section-title -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%; color: #ffffff;\">(\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd ngay \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh giao ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u01a1n 100.000 h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfng Anh. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ea1n \u2026 )<\/span><\/p>\n<div role=\"form\" class=\"wpcf7\" id=\"wpcf7-f284-o1\" lang=\"vi\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"><\/div>\n<form action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/29#wpcf7-f284-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf